Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: US budget deficit
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043wt34
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 Dec 1981
President Reagan faces unpleasant forecast of further deficits over his plans for the economy. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less